Summary Calendar.*

United States Court of Appeals, Fifth Circuit. June 18, 1971. Varón & Stahl, P. A., Hollywood, Fla., for petitioner-appellant. *112Earl Faircloth, Atty. Gen., of Fla., Tallahassee, Fla., Charles W.
